<p style="font-size: 18px; margin-bottom: 24px;">Hi <%= @name %>,</p>

<% if @waived %>
  <p>Thank you so much for your incredible generosity. By choosing to waive your refund, you're directly supporting our community during this transition.</p>
  <p>Your kindness means more than words can express. You're helping us ensure that every pass holder who needs a refund can receive one.</p>
<% else %>
  <p>Thank you for submitting your refund request. We've received your information and will process it as quickly as possible.</p>
<% end %>

<div style="background-color: #302117; border: 1px solid #5B2E12; border-radius: 8px; padding: 24px; text-align: center; margin: 24px 0;">
  <p style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px; margin: 0 0 8px;">Your Confirmation Number</p>
  <p style="font-size: 32px; font-weight: 700; color: #F45D00; font-family: monospace; letter-spacing: 2px; margin: 0;"><%= @confirmation_number %></p>
</div>

<p style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;">Please save this confirmation number. You'll need it to check your request status.</p>

<h2 style="color: #F45D00; font-size: 18px; margin: 32px 0 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; padding-bottom: 8px;">Request Details</h2>

<table role="presentation" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0" border="0" width="100%">
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131;">
      <span style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;">Decision</span>
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; text-align: right;">
      <span style="color: #E8E0D8; font-weight: 600;"><%= @decision_text %></span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <% if @amount_paid %>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131;">
      <span style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;">Original Ticket Price</span>
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; text-align: right;">
      <span style="color: #E8E0D8; font-weight: 600;">$<%= sprintf("%.2f", @amount_paid) %></span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <% end %>
  <% if @refund_amount && !@waived %>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131;">
      <span style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;">Refund Amount</span>
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; text-align: right;">
      <span style="color: #E8E0D8; font-weight: 600;">$<%= sprintf("%.2f", @refund_amount) %></span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <% end %>
  <% if @donated_amount %>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131;">
      <span style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;"><%= @waived ? "Amount Waived" : "Amount Donated" %></span>
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; text-align: right;">
      <span style="color: #228B22; font-weight: 600;">$<%= sprintf("%.2f", @donated_amount) %></span>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <% end %>
  <tr>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0;">
      <span style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px;">Status</span>
    </td>
    <td style="padding: 12px 0; text-align: right;">
      <% if @waived %>
        <span style="color: #228B22; font-weight: 600;">Waived</span>
      <% else %>
        <span style="color: #F45D00; font-weight: 600;">Submitted</span>
      <% end %>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>

<% if @waived %>
  <div style="background-color: #302117; border: 1px solid #5B2E12; border-radius: 8px; padding: 20px; margin: 24px 0;">
    <p style="color: #F45D00; font-weight: 600; margin: 0 0 8px;">You're making a difference</p>
    <p style="color: #E8E0D8; margin: 0; font-size: 14px;">Your name will appear on our Community Support wall on the progress page as a thank you for your generosity.</p>
  </div>
<% else %>
  <h2 style="color: #F45D00; font-size: 18px; margin: 32px 0 16px; border-bottom: 1px solid #313131; padding-bottom: 8px;">What Happens Next?</h2>

  <ol style="padding-left: 20px; margin: 0;">
    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.6;">We'll verify your information against our records.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.6;">Once verified, we'll begin processing your refund via Zelle.</li>
    <li style="margin-bottom: 12px; line-height: 1.6;">You'll receive an email when your refund has been sent.</li>
  </ol>
<% end %>

<p style="margin-top: 32px; text-align: center;">
  <a href="<%= @status_url %>" style="display: inline-block; background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F45D00 0%, #A25A3C 100%); color: #ffffff; text-decoration: none; padding: 14px 28px; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; font-size: 16px;">Check Your Status</a>
</p>

<p style="color: #9A8F85; font-size: 14px; margin-top: 32px;">If you have any questions, don't hesitate to reach out to us on Facebook.</p>

<p style="margin-top: 24px;">With gratitude,<br><strong style="color: #F45D00;">The Neo Kizomba Festival Team</strong></p>
